Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.50,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}本字幕由DHR百合組製作 僅供交流參考\N\N如喜歡本作品請支持正版
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:05.00,Staff,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)}翻譯：東條路易\N\N後期：Misaki喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.08,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,世上的魚類某日忽然全失去了蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,至今10年仍無人知曉原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.84,0:00:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,人們為滿足一嚐鮮美海味之慾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,以日本的科技力 在字宙打造魚塭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,由尾道的漁師開啟了宇宙漁業的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,加上兩性工作平等法的抬頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,為增進女性從事宇宙漁業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,從國內外招募了6名宇宙漁師儲備人員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:10.92,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(770,585)}到宇宙捕魚去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 小春正為了宇宙漁師的夢想邁出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.01,0:02:19.22,Default,,0,0,660,,{\fs40}福山 福山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,妹妹 妳要去尾道的話要在這站換車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的包包
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.31,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姨 丟得好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓奶奶吃到最愛吃的壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我會去宇宙捕獲一大堆壽司配料的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拍照傳給奶奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好像比我想得更都市化？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我聞到海風的味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,這張也傳過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\c&H585858&\bord0\pos(627,230)}傳    送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\c&H585858&\bord0\pos(638,315)}奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\c&H585858&\bord0\pos(638,382)}其他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:18.57,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\c&H585858&\bord0\pos(600,380)}已 發 送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去市公所報到之前還有很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.50,Default,,0,0,660,,{\fs40}讓您等候多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,660,,{\fs40}感謝各位旅客今天搭乘千光寺山纜車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:42.51,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※千光寺公園西側觀景台（千光寺山公園西展望台）。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有寺廟跟神社 還有很多造船廠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.93,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※並列的尾道大橋與新尾道大橋同為島並海道（しまなみ海道/西瀬戸自動車道）\N　的部分道路，靠近太平洋一側的是尾道大橋。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那座嶠就是島並海道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,火箭 從這裡也看得見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,尾漁2號…宇宙漁師就是搭乘它…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好想快點搭乘它飛上宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好想捕魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我燃起幹勁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:27.30,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※千白稻荷神社。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:30.01,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※千光寺山公園鼓岩（千光寺山公園つづみ岩）\N　{\fs30}該岩石經敲打會發出類似皮鼓的聲音而得此名，亦是「有名畫家寫生地」（畫面右下字樣）之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:33.31,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※西國寺\N　{\fs30}畫面中的西國寺三重塔為日本國家指定重要文化遺產。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶喜歡這種有氣質的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小黑貓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,別跑啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你在等我嗎 好聰明哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還有你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,來 笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,撩得貓奴心花怒放 這是何等高超的技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,跟丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她都遲到35分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,空町春到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.76,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,車站員有看過貌似空町的女生2小時前就出了剪票口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼久之前？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,手機還沒聯絡上她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我打了好幾次電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我們也去需忙找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.65,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※Boku是日語男性第一人稱。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,「我們」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.44,0:06:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的女高中生都自稱Boku的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妳冷靜點 鳴海
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.95,0:06:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,美劍真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫櫻舞湖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,您忘記了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 妳們兩個是第一次來尾道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要是連妳們都迷路就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡多等一下子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,手機沒電了 還流了滿身汗好不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 換套衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不能讓我們加入宇宙漁捕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那對大小姐妳們來說還太困難了 請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.83,0:07:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,無論駕駛飛魚或漁捕的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.67,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們都不比男性漁師差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這話可不能當做沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,女人要去宇宙漁捕還早了一百萬年啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這表情是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,鍵谷 麻煩你理性用事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,漁會理事長說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你收斂點 鍵谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,風祭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐…不是 波乃妳也要適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還在受訓期間就去宇宙漁捕是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,妳聽見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,而且妳們只有兩個人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙漁捕需要三人一組才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,連這點事都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,居然還敢說想去宇宙漁捕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,660,,{\fs40}鍵谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,波乃 今天就先打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,請問尾道市公所在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡要搭火東到尾道 沿海邊走很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,什磨 我就是從尾道車站走過來的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在哪走錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是新來的宇宙漁師儲備人員對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫空町春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是向島人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:38.47,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※兩種讀音都寫作「向島」，但前者是廣島縣的向島，後者才是東京都的向島。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不是Mukaishima 是Mukoujima…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在咕噥什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妳是向島人的話 應該也很會游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我還曾在全國大賽上得過冠軍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那飛魚呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,飛魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我超喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,像小鳥一樣好帥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就湊齊三個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,請讓我們參加宇宙漁捕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這、這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼想去的話就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,鍵谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是擺平女子部的機會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可是風險太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,要是有什麼萬一就拚上性命保護她們囉 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 我想趕快去市公所了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,待會我們要出發去宇宙魚塭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,空町春要跟波乃和真紀子一起去宇宙漁捕？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,現在接電話的是我萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,漁會理事長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,空町春是還沒受過任何訓練的外行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,請立刻制止她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法？ 已經搭上火箭了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,階段燃燒循環 液氧 液氫 已就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-2}Second stage liquid oxygen and hydrogen systems are ready
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch deck water curtain start
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所有系統已就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All systems ready
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,主引擎點火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Main engine ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,SRB 點火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,125,0,,{\fs30}火箭助推器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,SRB ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,升空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And lift off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,SRB 分離
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.46,0:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,SRB jettison
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 我要飛去宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,列隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,現在進行本次漁業任務的概要確認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好慢 妳不能快點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我會幫妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我竟穿著這套憧憬的裝備身在宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直像宇宙漁師一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是薪真紀子 19歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,村上波乃 17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我同年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 那麼跩我還以為妳跟MAKIMAKI差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,妳這人真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有那個意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還有她不叫MAKIMAKI 是薪真紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.02,0:11:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,叫MAKIMAKI也行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天會借3架飛魚給共同參加的女子部儲備人員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,飛魚可是新型的突擊宇宙船 可別弄壞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.87,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H7A6D61&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fr8\pos(620,100)}注意頭頂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:53.87,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7BCDF&\3c&H2326B9&\fr-90\fn@方正准圆_GBK\pos(1200,230)}島並船塢入口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,以1號魚塭為漁場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就位之後 用魚群探測器搜尋宇宙魚群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,並操縱飛魚將其捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,注意不要掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,以上 現在出航前往1號魚塭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是飛魚的駕駛艙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,各自趁現在選好守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…請問守護神是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是有看過手冊了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這根本沒法開始啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們女子部自己想辦法處理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,守護神是支援宇宙漁師的重要夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,總之妳先從神明APP裡選一尊守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,神明APP？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,妳不會連用來召喚守護神的APP都還沒下載吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,「嗯 對」妳個大頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,太誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,手機借我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我手機沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真紀子 交給妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去吧 這裡有備用電池
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,MAKIMAKI謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,再15分鐘後進入1號魚塭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛是說先把手機固定在架上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,再碰下旁遇的按鈕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,然後按旁邊的按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,手機放上去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:17.79,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic X P Heavy\fs30\c&H28281E&\bord0\pos(230,120)}然後按旁邊的按鈕…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.50,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic X P Heavy\fs40\c&H28281E&\bord0\pos(395,137)}哎。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:19.50,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fnGen Jyuu Gothic X P Heavy\fs40\c&H28281E&\bord0\pos(282,250)}妳還知道這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小春現在碰觸的是通訊按鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了守護神 短距離的話在水中也能通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有情況發生時記得要用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就用神明APP選擇八百萬神社裡的守護神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我召喚奧丁 真紀子召喚闇神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,妳選其他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,奧丁和闇神以外的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就決定是這位守護神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是MISAKI大人蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,居然召喚了我 妳很有挑守護神的眼光嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒有那麼厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.42,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是小春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,居然偏偏挑到最派不上用場的守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真紀子 別管她了我們兩個去捕魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也、也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小春 別在意 妳要相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,說得也是 既然選了就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,總感覺有點無法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這股氣勢蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就是宇宙魚塭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,前方有魚群反應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,全員準備離艦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全機出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,照我說的做就沒問題了蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等正前方的信號變成藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,放開右手的操縱焊 油門踩到底就行了蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 MISA蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對守護神的我稱呼MISA蹦成何體統蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼關係 很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不說了 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那些從大家的飛魚發出的光是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要召喚出守護神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,突擊宇宙船便會被神息包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠使用守護神的漁具蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,守護神的漁具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,MISA蹦有什麼漁具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我說完蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒有漁具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能比魚群探測器更快發現宇宙魚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,還能查知危險呢蹦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是守護神嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,專心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有巨大反應 已經很接近魚群了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我說MISA蹦 你不是能探測嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是小春手機的感測器有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.98,0:16:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,奧丁 漁具降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,闇神 漁具降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,MISA蹦 你不是能查知危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有危險接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,MISA蹦真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上接著說也沒意義啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,660,,{\fs40}小春 旁邊！旁邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝MAKIMAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,風祭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,波乃 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也可以搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,天鳥船神 讓大小姐見識下真正的宇宙漁捕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你走慢了 風祭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,該上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,吉祥天 黃金豬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好事將至
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,伊邪那美命 神通力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,來玩吧來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,天鳥船神 神通力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是大好心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,捕獲網發射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,捕獲完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好 去找下個獵物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是宇宙漁師的合作無間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這座魚塭的霸主出現了 很接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,謝了 波乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.81,0:19:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,螃蟹
